get the fuck into the woods, Bubs!

24:09.322 --> 24:10.949
We're fine here!
We're okay.

24:11.032 --> 24:12.033
Let's go!
Everybody out!

24:14.619 --> 24:16.496
[Bubbles] "Yeah,
this will be easy," you said.

24:16.580 --> 24:18.456
Now we're in a fucking foot pursuit!

24:18.540 --> 24:20.542
Grab a fucking bag of mushrooms!
Go! Go! Go!

24:20.625 --> 24:22.752
[Bubbles whimpering]

24:24.921 --> 24:27.007
[Bubbles] Fuck, I think
we lost them, boys.

24:27.090 --> 24:29.259
Fucking sucks about my car
but I guess I'll get another one.

24:29.342 --> 24:30.552
How the fuck do you expect

24:30.635 --> 24:32.929
