-That's it, Randy!
-Okay, that's enough.

29:16.629 --> 29:17.881
Might be too early for that.

29:18.089 --> 29:20.216
I love you, Randy.
All right.

29:21.092 --> 29:23.636
-Thanks, Julian.
-Thanks, Julian.

29:23.720 --> 29:25.472
-Have a good night, fel...
-Whew.

29:25.555 --> 29:26.639
Ricky, Rick!

29:26.723 --> 29:28.558
[whispering] He shit himself.
He shit himself.

29:29.392 --> 29:31.728
